==English==

===Adjective===
'''centauroid'''

# Of or pertaining to something resembling a centaur in shape &mdash; particularly, a creature having a humanoid torso adjoining a quadrupedal body.
#:'''1974:''' "'Centauroid' was a very loose description.  The burly two-armed torso merged smoothly with the four-legged barrel..." &mdash; Poul Anderson,  ''Fire Time''